definition.value: One of three isomeric monoterpenes differing in the positions of their two double bonds (alpha- and beta-terpinene being the others). In gamma-terpinene the double bonds are at the 1- and 4-positions of the p-menthane skeleton.
A sphingomyelin 36:3 in which the fatty acyl and sphingoid portions are specified as oleoyl and (4E,14Z)-sphingadienine respectively.
